  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<strong>Sorcerer Bloodline</strong><br/><br/><p>Your family has a connection with the ethereal substance known as ectoplasm, whether from communing with the spirits or battling the spiritual undead. The power of the Ethereal Plane thrums in your mind and pulls at your flesh.</p><p><b>Class Skill: </b>Stealth.</p><p><b>Bonus Spells: </b>obscuring mist (3rd), ghost whip (5th), ectoplasmic snare (7th), spirit-bound blade (9th), wall of ectoplasm (11th), ethereal jaunt (13th), ectoplasmic eruption (15th), create demiplane (17th), etherealness (19th).</p><p><b>Bonus Feats: </b>Blind-Fight, Dodge, Ectoplasmic SpellAPG, Lingering SpellAPG, Silent Spell, Skill Focus (Fly), Skill Focus (Stealth), Spell Focus.</p><p><b>Bloodline Arcana: </b>Incorporeal creatures take 75% of the normal amount of damage from your damaging spells, and when incorporeal creatures attempt saving throws against your non-damaging spells, they roll twice and must take the lower result.</p><p><b>Bloodline Powers: </b>You can control and emit ectoplasm, leaving you less grounded in the physical world.</p>",
